resources.string: Ngokuvula Ngesigxivizo Somunwe, ungavula ifoni yakho usebenzisa isigxivizo sakho somunwe. Ngokuphepha, le nketho idinga ukukhiya kwesikrini okuyisipele.

"Inzwa yesigxivizo somunwe ikwinkinobho Yamandla.
Thinta kancane inkinobho ngaphandle kokuyicindezela."
Phakamisa, bese uthinta. Hambisa umunwe wakho kancane isikhathi ngasinye.

Ukuvula Ngesigxivizo Somunwe kudala imodeli ehlukile yesigxivizo sakho somunwe ukuqinisekisa ukuthi nguwe. Ukuze wenze imodeli yesigxivizo somunwe ngesikhathi sokusethwa, uzothatha izithombe zesigxivizo sakho somunwe kusukela kuzindawo ezihlukile.

Lapho usebenzisa Ukuvula Ngesigxivizo Somunwe, imifanekiso isetshenziselwa ukuvuselela imodeli yakho yesigxivizo somunwe. Imifanekiso esetshenziselwe ukusungula imodeli yesigxivizo somunwe wakho ayilokothi igcinwe, kodwa imodeli yesigxivizo somunwe igcinwa ngokuphephile kufoni yakho futhi ayilokothi ishiye ifoni. Konke ukucubungula kwenzeka ngokuphepha kufoni yakho.
Ungasula imodeli yakho yesigxivizo somunwe, noma uvale Ukuvula Isigxivizo Somunwe noma kunini Kumasethingi. Amamodeli wesigxivizo somunwe namamodeli kugcinwa kwifoni kuze kube yilapho uzisula.

Ukuvula ngesigxivizo somunwe kudala imodeli ehlukile yesigxivizo seminwe sengane yakho ukuqinisekisa ukuthi iyona. Ukudala le modeli yesigxivizo seminwe ngesikhathi sokusetha, bazothatha izithombe zesigxivizo sabo seminwe kusukela kuzimo ezihlukile.

Uma isebenzisa Ukuvula Kwesigxivizo Somunwe, imifanekiso isetshenziselwa ukubuyekeza imodeli yayo yesigxivizo somunwe. Izithombe ezisetshenziselwe ukusungula imodeli yesigxivizo somunwe yengane yakho azilokothi zigcinwe, kodwa imodeli yesigxivizo seminwe igcinwa ngokuphephile kwifoni futhi ayilokothi ishiye ifoni. Konke ukucubungula kwenzeka ngokuphepha kwifoni.
Wena nengane yakho ningasula imodeli yesigxivizo somunwe wayo, noma uvale Ukuvula Ngesigxivizo Somunwe noma kunini Kumasethingi. Amamodeli esigxivizo sominwe agcinwa efonini aze asulwe.
Inzwa yesigxivizo somunwe esenkinobhweni yamandla. Yinkinobho emfushane ohlangothini lwefoni.
Hambisa umunwe wakho kancane isikhathi ngasinye.
Qhubeka nokunyakaza ukuze uthwebule ezinye izindawo zesigxivizo sakho somunwe
Lokhu kwenza ukuvula ngephutha kungabi bikho kangako. Lapho lesethingi isivaliwe, ukuthinta kancane inzwa kuzovuleka.
